{"tid":441865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆：Uber如依法例申請「出租車牌照」便可以合法經營","createTime":"2017-10-20T05:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T06:47:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b38010d1680a498a4e1d6b51f9fb446fbc601ee","tid":441865,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:18:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1360317-20171020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1360317-20171020.htm&d=yxF5I2YAp5zYew9dlCv25BxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=11c74978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1360317-20171020.htm&h=2d00d44d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1360317-20171020.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.marketing-interactive.com.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Uber_busshelter1-e1472611704475-700x421.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.marketing-interactive.com.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2FUber_busshelter1-e1472611704475-700x421.png&h=cfaeec9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長陳帆說，政府從無限制網約車的安排，如果透過載客取酬，法例就有所限制，Uber如果依香港法例要求便可以合法經營，包括申請出租車牌照，如果某公司不想依香港法律，堅持自己的方法，除非修改本港法例，否則都需依法行事。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨的譚文豪在立法會交通事務委員會會議上質疑，現時出租車牌照的門檻及規例，未能迎合現時的營運模式。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆說，政府要考慮本港公共交通運輸、生態平衡及管理，不能騷擾既有效率及順暢。他說Uber也不是全世界通行，不少東南亞國家及英國倫敦亦禁止Uber運作。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署署長陳美寶說，政府今年已優化出租車牌照的申請，強調政府如果要批出新牌照，同時要處理乘客安全及保險問題。"},{"pid":"7736f2e7017411239ecbd94f2e40eaa918086498","tid":441865,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"轎車牌？"},{"pid":"754169b11cf6688f443a261a332e9efb0a573aeb","tid":441865,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"054f4448f500c213aa02319060474f4158676911","tid":441865,"uid":86841,"